{"tid":2249404,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【6.9 立法會衝突】認非法集結罪　兩人被錢禮判入教導所　另三人判囚 4 個月","createTime":"2020-10-19T10:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T10:12:29.000Z","uid":184261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fe9560212884226969d99eb6b535188e53539fc9","tid":2249404,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:08:47.000Z","msg":"去年 6 月 9 日，過百萬人參與民陣發起的反修例遊行。翌日（10 日）凌晨，示威者與警方在立法會大樓一帶發生衝突，多人被控。當中 5 名男子早前在東區裁判法院承認一項非法集結，還押至今日（19 日）判刑。主任裁判官錢禮指案件涉及暴力及破壞社會安寧，判刑須具阻嚇性，認為判處社會服務令並不適合，須判處監禁，經考慮後最終判處兩名 19 歲及 20 歲的被告入教導所，兩人的律師均表示將會就判刑提出覆核；另外三名被告則各判囚 4 個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/6-9-%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E8%AA%8D%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E7%BD%AA-%E5%85%A9%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%A4%E5%85%A5%E6%95%99%E5%B0%8E%E6%89%80-%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-4-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88/?fbclid=IwAR3bcqvL7YpnAz_ABc_HvSna_RCAOqZvjon5_gV1SUtAdPadsblgiBh52tg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F6-9-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%2589%2580-%25E5%258F%25A6%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-4-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3bcqvL7YpnAz_ABc_HvSna_RCAOqZvjon5_gV1SUtAdPadsblgiBh52tg&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=6182fe9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F6-9-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%2589%2580-%25E5%258F%25A6%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA